Introduction

  Major differences in Mac vs. Windows operating systems

     * Bridging these differences will help Macs and PCs work together
       better
     * Will discuss hardware and software solutions for using Macs and PCs
     * Will discuss problems to watch out for when working cross-platform

  Important note!

     Certain commercial equipment and software are identified in these
     web pages. Such identification does not imply recommendation or
     endorsement by NIH, nor does it imply that the products identified
     are necessarily the best available for the procedures described.
